                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When investigating &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6092&quot; title=&quot;testPositionAgressive(org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.jdbcapi.BlobClob4BlobTest)j fails with : &amp;#39;The handle is invalid.: java.io.IOException&amp;#39;.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-6092&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-6092&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I found some code that could be simplified/cleaned up. Will make those changes here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
